WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.280 --> 00:00:03.840
Add a menu option to view 
the user's preferred location on a map.

00:00:04.310 --> 00:00:08.080
It will be handled by any maps app 
that's available on your device.

00:00:08.900 --> 00:00:12.540
If there is no map app on your device, 
handle this case gracefully

00:00:12.540 --> 00:00:15.510
to avoid a crash. 
You might want to recall that

00:00:15.510 --> 00:00:18.530
we use SharedPreferences 
to store the preferred location.

